{"type": "article", "id": 57973, "title": "传“网红电商第一股”明年赴美上市，以及，Palace 与 Ralph Lauren 合作系列发售在即  | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-11-05T07:33:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 53949, "name": "网红电商"}, {"id": 53950, "name": "红蜻蜓"}, {"id": 28455, "name": "Palace"}, {"id": 14120, "name": "Rapha"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181104204902FnYC7J9sG1daxQPf.png", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.zhitongcaijing.com/content/detail/160990.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">传如涵控股 2019 年将赴美上市</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 根据自媒体“IPO 早知道”11 月 1 日消息，在线时尚公司如涵控股计划 2019 年赴美上市，预计募资 1 亿- 2 亿美元。</p><p>如涵控股成立于 2011 年，今年于内地新三板退市。其主要业务是发掘网红，再到淘宝等网上电商平台宣传产品及开设网店。截止至 2018 年 8 月 4 日，如涵旗下三大网红张大奕、大金、管阿姨微博粉丝数分别为 674 万、263 万、202 万，其相应淘宝店铺粉丝数分别为 814 万、286 万、119 万。张大奕 2017 年“双十一”当天的销售额超过 1.7 亿元人民币。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://tech.163.com/18/1104/11/DVOV2VNN00098IEO.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">天猫与太古地产在京签约</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 双方于 11 月 3 日下午举行了签约仪式。天猫表示计划在北京三里屯太古里、北京颐堤港、上海兴业太古汇、广州太古汇和成都远洋太古里先后开设天猫智慧门店、天猫理想站、明星应援站、天猫智能母婴室、智慧停车等 5 个商业项目。</p><p>根据通稿中的解释，天猫理想站将“带来超前 3 至 5 年的近未来店铺体验”，明星应援站是“国内首个新零售明星应援拍照打卡网红点”，天猫智能母婴室将“关照母婴出行体验和需求，并提供 1 分钱领样母婴必需品服务”，智慧停车“实现无感支付，快速离场”。<br></p><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.ellechina.com/fashion/news/20181102-290612.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\">国内女鞋品牌红蜻蜓宣布由 Angelababy 担任代言人</a>&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;有 23 年历史的国内女鞋品牌红蜻蜓于 10 月底在上海举办了品牌战略升级发布会。除了在发布会上宣布由 Angelababy 担任代言人，该品牌还在发布会上推出了与其合作的明星系列产品，并宣布未来将向年轻化、休闲化、街头化方向转型。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>离圣诞节还有一个多月，各品牌已经开始陆续推出相关广告。<a href=\"https://www.teenvogue.com/story/selena-gomez-coach-holiday-ad-video\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Coach 刚刚发布了以“Lights, Camera, Holiday”为主题的假日广告片</strong></a>，由 Selena Gomez 与一些动画角色共同出演。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104200551UbH2PelJm7vxftou.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.680317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=n078337t5hd\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/palace-polo-ralph-lauren-collaboration/#slide-10\" rel=\"nofollow\">英国街头品牌 Palace 与 Polo Ralph Lauren 的联名系列即将发售。</a></strong></p><p>欧洲及北美地区将于 11 月 9 日上架，日本和韩国地区将于 11 月 10 日上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104192849FrvemnKtjcAldQ30.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811041928513SYa7OLQIus4ANjM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104192851hSLGgMornzwiZJYx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104192849wPBNG4xqFgKnpEkd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104192850VKzpjgJv8ArXImSQ.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.707353\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104192847C5snfcoD3lH7WmZa.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.707353\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104192850YBo4PdWKIRVc0Q6X.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.707353\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104192850kLlmX7106xAqeJ8w.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.707353\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104192850RPTtnk6uqjdGWLlm.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.707353\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104192850DVaNx4Rpf0sAPgFZ.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.707353\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811041928508Uq0YdlGmQXzLM74.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.707353\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.manrepeller.com/2018/11/sleepleisure-is-a-cozy-new-fashion-trend.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">时尚网站 Man Repeller 推出了一期特辑，演示睡衣休闲风格（Sleepleisure）的秋冬穿搭</a></strong>。</p><p>Sleepleisure 演化自 Rihanna 创造的浴袍休闲风格（bathleisure），后者的重要元素包括浴帽和头巾。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104193415kiJ3q2Oe5MgwE9mx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104193413bJIyxiUMLKlQOHnz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104193412Mxdzk4FAcuhDfSnY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104193415Mm1gH5b9TEwFhaD6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.487106\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104193415HSQmjUgCOx9RBvWG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104193415usSgCexj8iID1GlN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104193416edIhvW1V3PaUZ4tc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104193416mHoqBhF7uPgzfUwE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811041934175Qf7qcv1yYZkHs9x.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104193416yeptZAcIkKLP3Rg1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811041934176EYAZwfV4GNtBpsQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104193413ViPCIpobzDHcF41k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104193416EjXIDAi1y3NceqxB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104193416VPN2FLQBAMctdU34.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811041934183JLYme98qhZa2Cg6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/cait-oppermann-rapha-photography-011118\" rel=\"nofollow\">纽约摄影师&nbsp;Cait Oppermann 为英国高端骑行品牌 Rapha 拍摄了一组大片</a></strong>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104194029HUWPKIQuEjVeOBvq.png\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104194028Dy9ScszjqwJ6VYiZ.png\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104194029ZyN5OWuc4aIrREV0.png\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811041940297iProjMXJWwUv5GQ.png\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104194031zDC0vL58w3jW1oSP.png\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104194032epL7Q9jlXcVTWEqP.png\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104194032IMwJF8enLrqEY6ui.png\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181104194033mc84uv7WIQpH3fXh.png\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"p